  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I heard you watched Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani. Did you catch the latest scene where they dance by the lake?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "No, I missed that part. I watched it a few days back, but I got busy with work. Was the dance scene good? I heard the music is catchy."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You missed the lake dance — it’s one of the best parts! The music is catchy, and the visuals are stunning. Did you enjoy the movie overall?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I liked the movie overall. The story was okay, but the songs were really good. I watched it with my friends, and we laughed a lot. Have you seen it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You liked the songs — that’s the best part! I haven’t seen it yet, but I’ve heard the comedy is great. What’s your favourite song from the movie?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite song is \"Agar Tum Sath Ho.\" It's very peppy and makes you want to dance. The lyrics are also nice. Have you listened to it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You picked a great one — Agar Tum Sath Ho is fun and full of energy. I haven’t listened to it yet, but I’ll give it a try. What made you like the lyrics?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The lyrics are simple but meaningful. They talk about love and friendship, which I can relate to. Also, the way it's sung makes it very catchy. Maybe I should listen to it again sometime. Have you heard a good Hindi song recently?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said the lyrics are simple but meaningful — that’s the best kind. I haven’t heard a new song yet, but I’d love to know one you recommend. What’s on your playlist these days?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Recently I’ve been listening to \"Chogada\" from the movie Dhadak. It's very peppy and fun. My friends also like it. Do you know it? If not, I can describe it."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said \"Chogada\" is peppy and fun — that’s exactly what I look for in a song! I haven’t heard it yet, so a quick description would help. What makes it so catchy for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The song has a cool beat and a lot of energy. It's about young love and having fun. The way the singers use their voices and the background music makes it really catchy. I listen to it when I want to feel happy. Let me know if you try it!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said the beat and energy make it catchy — and that it’s about young love — sounds perfect for a mood lift. I’ll give it a listen. What made you choose it today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I chose it because I was feeling a bit tired after work, and it helped me feel more energetic. Music is a great mood booster for me — it helps me relax or get motivated, depending on what I need. Have you found a song that does that for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said music helps you relax and get motivated — I agree, it’s a great tool. I haven’t found my perfect mood booster yet, but I’d love to hear one you suggest. What’s your go-to song for energy?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My go-to song for energy is \"Naach Meri Rani\" from the movie \"Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon.\" It's very lively and has a cool, modern vibe. Whenever I need to feel active or happy, I play this. The beat is strong, and the lyrics are fun. You should give it a try!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said the song is lively and has a modern vibe — that’s exactly what I need! I’ll put it on my list. What made you pick it as your go-to?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I picked it because it’s upbeat and makes me want to move. Sometimes after a long day at work, I just need something that makes me smile — this song does that. The rhythm is hard to ignore! Also, the singer’s voice adds to the energy. Maybe I’ll share a playlist sometime."
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said the rhythm is hard to ignore — I believe it! Music that makes you smile is the best kind. A playlist would be fun to see. What else do you have on there?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I have a mix of peppy songs and some calm ones too — maybe next time I can share it with you. For now, I should get back to work. Thanks for the conversation, Maya! Talk to you later."
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said you have both peppy and calm songs — that sounds like a perfect balance. Take it easy at work. Talk soon!"
    }
  ],
